author: David O'Shaughnessy
title: TV | Nine Stone Lighter: Reality Bites
text: This Reality Bites special follows actor, writer and producer Jules Coll as she undergoes gastric bypass surgery after years of struggling with her weight. The operation, while familiar to many, is no small procedure and requires a lifetime of dedicated eating habits, and this documentary follows Jules all the way as she proves it's never too late to change your life.
